INSERT INTO [DataWarehouse].[Stage].[aTao_Application]
           ([Application_Id]
           ,[Version]
           ,[Name]
           ,[Description]
           ,[AuthenticationContext]
           ,[ApplicationType]
           ,[ControllerContext]
           ,[DefaultSequence]
           ,[LoginSequence]
           ,[Locator]
           ,[IsExternal]
           ,[IsDefault]
           ,[IsHmc]
           ,[IsBaselineHourly]
           ,[Client_Id]
           ,[Role_Id]
           ,[DateCreated]
           ,[DateLastModified]
           ,[CreatedBy]
           ,[LastModifiedBy]
           ,[ApplicationCategory]
           ,[ExtractDate]
           ,[BatchDate]
           ,[SourceSkey])

	SELECT
		APPLICATION_ID
		, VERSION
		, NAME
		, DESCRIPTION
		, AUTHENTICATIONCONTEXT
		, APPLICATIONTYPE
		, CONTROLLERCONTEXT
		, DEFAULTSEQUENCE
		, LOGINSEQUENCE
		, LOCATOR
		, ISEXTERNAL
		, ISDEFAULT
		, NULL AS ISHMC /* REMOVED FOR 8.5 */
		, NULL AS ISBASELINEHOURLY /* REMOVED FOR 8.5 */
		, CLIENT_ID
		, ROLE_ID
		,DATECREATED
		,DATELASTMODIFIED
		, CREATEDBY
		, LASTMODIFIEDBY
		,APPLICATIONCATEGORY,
		 <BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate,
		 <BATCHDATE> as BatchDate,
		 <SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey

	FROM OPENQUERY( <LINKNAME> , N'
		SELECT
			APPLICATION_ID
			, VERSION
			, NAME
			, DESCRIPTION
			, AUTHENTICATIONCONTEXT
			,APPLICATIONTYPE
			, CONTROLLERCONTEXT
			, DEFAULTSEQUENCE
			, LOGINSEQUENCE
			, LOCATOR
			, ISEXTERNAL
			, ISDEFAULT
			, NULL AS ISHMC /* REMOVED FOR 8.5 */
			, NULL AS ISBASELINEHOURLY /* REMOVED FOR 8.5 */
			, CLIENT_ID
			, ROLE_ID
			,TO_CHAR(DATECREATED,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS DATECREATED
			,TO_CHAR(DATELASTMODIFIED,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS DATELASTMODIFIED
			, CREATEDBY
			, LASTMODIFIEDBY
			,APPLICATIONCATEGORY
		FROM APPLICATION
		WHERE 
		(
		(DateLastModified >= <FROMDATE_Q> )
		 )
		') as a
SSIS_SQLText:
SELECT		
application_id, 
version, 
name, 
description, 
authenticationcontext, 
applicationtype, 
controllercontext, 
defaultsequence, 
loginsequence, 
locator, 
isexternal, 
isdefault, 
client_id, 
role_id, 
CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified,  
createdby, 
lastmodifiedby, 
applicationcategory, 
<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey
FROM application 
WHERE (datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

INSERT INTO [DataWarehouse].[Stage].[aTao_Availability]

           ,[StartDate]

           ,[MondayEndTime]
           ,[TuesdayStartTime]
           ,[TuesdayEndTime]
           ,[WednesdayStartTime]
           ,[WednesdayEndTime]
           ,[ThursdayStartTime]

           ,[SundayEndTime]

           ,[WillWorkWeekends]

           ,[WillWorkEvenings]

           ,[CustomField_Id]

	SELECT AVAILABILITY_ID
	   ,VERSION

	   ,WORKPREFERENCE
	   ,MONDAYSTARTTIME
	   ,MONDAYENDTIME
	   ,TUESDAYSTARTTIME
	   ,TUESDAYENDTIME
	   ,WEDNESDAYSTARTTIME
	   ,WEDNESDAYENDTIME
	   ,THURSDAYSTARTTIME
	   ,THURSDAYENDTIME
	   ,FRIDAYSTARTTIME
	   ,FRIDAYENDTIME
	   ,SATURDAYSTARTTIME
	   ,SATURDAYENDTIME
	   ,SUNDAYSTARTTIME
	   ,SUNDAYENDTIME
	   ,CANTWORK
	   ,CANTWORKDETAIL
	   ,WILLWORKHOLIDAYS
	   ,WILLWORKWEEKENDS
	   ,WILLWORKOVERTIME
	   ,WILLWORKEVENINGS
	   ,WILLWORKOVERNIGHT
	   ,WILLWORKEXTRAWORK
	   ,HOURSPERWEEK
	   ,DOCUMENT_ID
	   ,CUSTOMFIELD_ID
	   ,DATECREATED
	   ,DATELASTMODIFIED
	   ,CREATEDBY
	   ,LASTMODIFIEDBY
		,<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate
		,<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate
		,<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey
	FROM OPENQUERY(<LINKNAME>, N'
		SELECT AVAILABILITY_ID
		   ,VERSION
		   ,TO_CHAR(STARTDATE,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS STARTDATE
		   ,WORKPREFERENCE
		   ,MONDAYSTARTTIME
		   ,MONDAYENDTIME
		   ,TUESDAYSTARTTIME
		   ,TUESDAYENDTIME
		   ,WEDNESDAYSTARTTIME
		   ,WEDNESDAYENDTIME
		   ,THURSDAYSTARTTIME
		   ,THURSDAYENDTIME
		   ,FRIDAYSTARTTIME
		   ,FRIDAYENDTIME
		   ,SATURDAYSTARTTIME
		   ,SATURDAYENDTIME
		   ,SUNDAYSTARTTIME
		   ,SUNDAYENDTIME
		   ,CANTWORK
		   ,CANTWORKDETAIL
		   ,WILLWORKHOLIDAYS
		   ,WILLWORKWEEKENDS
		   ,WILLWORKOVERTIME
		   ,WILLWORKEVENINGS
		   ,WILLWORKOVERNIGHT
		   ,WILLWORKEXTRAWORK
		   ,HOURSPERWEEK
		   ,DOCUMENT_ID
		   ,CUSTOMFIELD_ID
		   ,TO_CHAR(DATECREATED,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS DATECREATED
		   ,TO_CHAR(DATELASTMODIFIED,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS DATELASTMODIFIED
		   ,CREATEDBY
		   ,LASTMODIFIEDBY
		FROM AVAILABILITY
		WHERE
			(DateLastModified >= <FROMDATE_Q> )
		') as a
SSIS_SQLText:
SELECT		availability_id, 
				version, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), startdate, 120) as startdate, 
				workpreference, 
				mondaystarttime, 
				mondayendtime, 
				tuesdaystarttime, 
				tuesdayendtime, 
				wednesdaystarttime, 
				wednesdayendtime, 
				thursdaystarttime, 
				thursdayendtime, 
				fridaystarttime, 
				fridayendtime, 
				saturdaystarttime, 
				saturdayendtime, 
				sundaystarttime, 
				sundayendtime, 
				cantwork, 
				cantworkdetail, 
				willworkholidays, 
				willworkweekends, 
				willworkovertime, 
				willworkevenings, 
				willworkovernight, 
				willworkextrawork, 
				hoursperweek, 
				document_id, 
				customfield_id, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
			    CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified, 
				createdby, 
				lastmodifiedby, 
				availabilitybits,
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM availability 
	 WHERE (datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

INSERT INTO [DataWarehouse].[Stage].[aTao_Client]

           ,[FAXNUMBER]

           ,[ExtractDate]
           ,[BatchDate]
           ,[SourceSkey])
	SELECT CLIENT_ID, 
		VERSION, 
		DAYSAPPLICATIONACTIVE, 
		DAYSAPPLICATIONEXCLUSIVE, 
		MILESSEARCHZIPCODE, 
		NAME, 
		DESCRIPTION,
		CITY,
		STATE,
		COUNTRY,
		ZIPCODE, 
		ADDRESS,
		NULL as WOTCPROVIDER,
		INLINEEMAIL,
		EMAILFULLADR,
		WEBGRADING, 
		WEBAPPTIMEOUT,
		NULL as QUESTIONSPERPAGE,
		WEBSAVE,
		MAXLOGINATTEMPTS,
		LOCKOUTDURATION,
		FAILEDLOGINRESETINTERVAL, 
		NULL as EPREDIX,
		NULL as HMCTIMEOUT,
		NULL as NONHIREABLEDURATION,
		NULL as MULTIPOSITION,
		DATECREATED,
		DATELASTMODIFIED,
		CREATEDBY,
		LASTMODIFIEDBY,
		PHONE,
		FAXNUMBER, 
		CUSTOMERID,
		PERMISSION_ID,
		<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate,
		<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate,
		<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey

	FROM OPENQUERY(<LINKNAME>, N'
		SELECT CLIENT_ID, 
			VERSION, 
			DAYSAPPLICATIONACTIVE, 
			DAYSAPPLICATIONEXCLUSIVE, 
			MILESSEARCHZIPCODE, 
			NAME, 
			DESCRIPTION,
			CITY,
			STATE,
			COUNTRY,
			ZIPCODE, 
			ADDRESS,
			NULL as WOTCPROVIDER,
			INLINEEMAIL,
			EMAILFULLADR,
			WEBGRADING, 
			WEBAPPTIMEOUT,
			NULL as QUESTIONSPERPAGE,
			WEBSAVE,
			MAXLOGINATTEMPTS,
			LOCKOUTDURATION,
			FAILEDLOGINRESETINTERVAL, 
			NULL as EPREDIX,
			NULL as HMCTIMEOUT,
			NULL as NONHIREABLEDURATION,
			NULL as MULTIPOSITION,
			TO_CHAR(DATECREATED,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS DATECREATED,
			TO_CHAR(DATELASTMODIFIED,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS DATELASTMODIFIED,
			CREATEDBY,
			LASTMODIFIEDBY,
			PHONE,
			FAXNUMBER, 
			CUSTOMERID,
			PERMISSION_ID
		FROM CLIENT	
		WHERE 
			(DateLastModified >= <FROMDATE_Q> )
		') as a
SSIS_SQLText:
SELECT	client_id, 
		version, 
		daysapplicationexclusive, 
		milessearchzipcode, 
		name, 
		description, 
		city, 
		state, 
		country, 
		zipcode, 
		address, 
		inlineemail, 
		emailfulladr, 
		webgrading, 
		webapptimeout, 
		websave, 
		maxloginattempts, 
		lockoutduration, 
		failedloginresetinterval, 
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified, 
		createdby, 
		lastmodifiedby, 
		phone, 
		faxnumber, 
		customerid, 
		permission_id, 
		fein, 
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), legalholdstartdate, 120) as legalholdstartdate, 
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), legalholdenddate, 120) as legalholdenddate, 
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), deactivationdate, 120) as deactivationdate, 
		customertype, 
		<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
		<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
		<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM client 
	 WHERE (datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

		,datecreated

		,createdby

           ,[DateLastModified]

           ,[BusinessRuleName]
           ,[HiringProcess_ID]
           ,[ExtractDate]

           ,[SourceSkey])
	select flowactivation_id
		,version
		,flowname

		,order_num
		,datecreated
		,datelastmodified
		,Createdby
		,lastmodifiedby
		,isrestartable
		,maxexecutions
		,businessrulename
		,hiringprocess_id
		,<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate
		,<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate
		,<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey
	FROM OPENQUERY( <LINKNAME> , N'
		select flowactivation_id
			,version
			,flowname
			,isactive
			,order_num
			,TO_CHAR(datecreated,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS datecreated
			,TO_CHAR(datelastmodified,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS datelastmodified

SSIS_SQLText:
SELECT		flowactivation_id, 
				version, 
				flowname, 
				isactive, 
				order_num, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified,  
				createdby, 
				lastmodifiedby, 
				isrestartable, 
				maxexecutions, 
				businessrulename,

INSERT INTO [DataWarehouse].[Stage].[aTao_JobBid_Response]
           ([JobBid_Response_Id]
           ,[Version]
           ,[Script_Id]
           ,[Response_Id]
           ,[JobBid_Id]
           ,[Workflow_Id]
           ,[Node_Id]
           ,[Answer]
           ,[ResponseGroup]
           ,[DateCreated]
           ,[DateLastModified]
           ,[CreatedBy]
           ,[LastModifiedBy]
           ,[ResponseRank]
           ,[WorkflowInstance_Id]
           ,[NodeInstance_Id]
           ,[ExtractDate]
           ,[BatchDate]
           ,[SourceSkey])
	SELECT 
		jobbid_response_id
		,version
		,script_id
		,response_id
		,jobbid_id
		,null as workflow_id
		,null as node_id
		,null as answer
		,responsegroup
		,datecreated
		,datelastmodified
		,createdby
		,lastmodifiedby
		,responserank
		,workflowinstance_id
		,nodeinstance_id
		,<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate
		,<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate
		,<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey
	FROM OPENQUERY(<LINKNAME>, N'
		SELECT
			 /*+ index(jbr IX_JOBBID_RESP_DATEMOD) index(r SYS_C009206) */ jbr.jobbid_response_id
			,jbr.version
			,jbr.script_id
			,jbr.response_id
			,jbr.jobbid_id
			,jbr.responsegroup
			,TO_CHAR(jbr.datecreated,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS datecreated
			,TO_CHAR(jbr.datelastmodified,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS datelastmodified
			,jbr.createdby
			,jbr.lastmodifiedby
			,jbr.responserank
			,jbr.workflowinstance_id
			,jbr.nodeinstance_id
		FROM
			script_question_atao sq
			inner join response_atao r
				on sq.question_id = r.question_id
			inner join jobbid_response jbr
				on sq.script_id = jbr.script_id
				and r.response_id = jbr.response_id
		WHERE 
			sq.knockoutreason is not null
			and jbr.DateLastModified >= <FROMDATE_Q> 
		') as a
SSIS_SQLText:
SELECT /*+ index(jbr IX_JOBBID_RESP_DATEMOD) index(r SYS_C009206) */ 
				jbr.jobbid_response_id, 
				jbr.version, 
				jbr.script_id, 
				jbr.response_id, 
				jbr.jobbid_id, 
				
				case when q.datameaning_id IS NOT NULL and r.answer_id IS NULL  				
				then CAST(jbr.answer AS NVARCHAR(510) ) else '' end answer,				 				
				jbr.responsegroup,			
				jbr.responsegroup, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), jbr.datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
			    CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), jbr.datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified, 
				jbr.createdby, 
				jbr.lastmodifiedby, 
				jbr.responserank, 
				jbr.workflowinstance_id, 
				jbr.nodeinstance_id, 
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
    FROM jobbid_response jbr 
	 INNER JOIN response_atao r 
	 ON jbr.response_id=r.response_id
	 INNER JOIN script_question_atao sq
	 ON sq.script_id = jbr.script_id AND sq.question_id = r.question_id 
	 INNER JOIN question_atao q ON r.question_id = q.question_id
	 WHERE (sq.knockoutreason IS NOT NULL OR q.datameaning_id IS NOT NULL) 
		AND (jbr.datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

INSERT INTO [DataWarehouse].[Stage].[aTao_JobBid_Workflow_History]
           ([JobBidWorkflowHistory_ID]
           ,[Version]
           ,[JobBid_ID]
           ,[FlowName]
           ,[NodeName]
           ,[EventType]
           ,[ProcessInstance_ID]
           ,[DateCreated]
           ,[DateLastModified]
           ,[CreatedBy]
           ,[LastModifiedBy]
           ,[ActionType]
           ,[NodeType]
           ,[WorkflowCategory]
           ,[ExtractDate]
           ,[BatchDate]
           ,[SourceSkey])

	select jobbid_workflow_history_id 
	  ,Version
	  ,JobBid_ID  
	  ,FlowName 
	  ,NodeName  
	  ,Event  
	  ,ProcessInstance_ID 
	  ,datecreated
	  ,DateLastModified
	  ,CreatedBy  
	  ,LastModifiedBy  
	  ,actiontype
	  ,NodeType  
	  ,WorkflowCategory
			,<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate
			,<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate
			,<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey
		FROM OPENQUERY(<LINKNAME>, N'
		select
			h.jobbid_workflow_history_id,  
			h.Version,  
			h.JobBid_ID,  
			h.FlowName,  
			h.NodeName,  
			h.Event,  
			h.ProcessInstance_ID,  
			TO_CHAR(datecreated,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS datecreated,
			TO_CHAR(h.DateLastModified,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS DateLastModified,
			h.CreatedBy,  
			h.LastModifiedBy,  
			h.actiontype,
			nv.stringvalue_ as NodeType,  
			case when nv.stringvalue_ is null then null 
			   else nc.stringvalue_ end as WorkflowCategory
		from 
			jobbid_workflow_history h
			left outer join JBPM_VariableInstance nv 
				on nv.processinstance_= h.processinstance_id
				and lower(nv.name_)=lower(h.nodename||'.nodetype')
			left outer join JBPM_VariableInstance nc 
				on nc.processinstance_= h.processinstance_id
				and lower(nc.name_)='workflowcategory'
		WHERE 
			(h.DateLastModified >= <FROMDATE_Q> )
		') as a
SSIS_SQLText:
SELECT		h.jobbid_workflow_history_id, 
				h.version, 
				h.jobbid_id, 
				h.flowname, 
				h.nodename, 
				h.event, 
				h.processinstance_id, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
			    CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), h.datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified, 
				h.createdby, 
				h.lastmodifiedby, 
				h.actiontype, 
				nv.stringvalue_ as nodetype, 
				CASE WHEN nv.stringvalue_ IS NULL THEN NULL ELSE nc.stringvalue_ END as workflowcategory, 
				h.isforautodisposition,
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM jobbid_workflow_history h with(nolock)
	 LEFT OUTER JOIN jbpm_variableinstance nv with(nolock)
	 ON nv.processinstance_= h.processinstance_id AND LOWER(nv.name_) = LOWER(h.nodename + '.nodetype') 
	 LEFT OUTER JOIN jbpm_variableinstance nc with(nolock)
	 ON nc.processinstance_= h.processinstance_id AND nc.name_ = 'workflowCategory'
	 WHERE (h.datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

INSERT INTO [DataWarehouse].[Stage].[aTao_Answer_aTao]
			([Answer_Id]
			,[Version]
			,[Description]
			,[Guuid]
			,[Datecreated]
			,[Createdby]
			,[Datelastmodified]
			,[Lastmodifiedby]
			,[Ss_External_Id]
			,[ExtractDate]
			,[BatchDate]
			,[SourceSkey])
SELECT ANSWER_ID
			,VERSION
			,DESCRIPTION
			,GUUID
			,DATECREATED
			,CREATEDBY
			,DATELASTMODIFIED
			,LASTMODIFIEDBY
			,SS_EXTERNAL_ID
			,<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate
			,<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate
			,<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey
FROM OPENQUERY(<LINKNAME>, N'
				SELECT ANSWER_ID, VERSION, DESCRIPTION, GUUID, TO_CHAR(DATECREATED,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS DATECREATED, 
					CREATEDBY, TO_CHAR(DATELASTMODIFIED,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS DATELASTMODIFIED, LASTMODIFIEDBY, SS_EXTERNAL_ID
				FROM ANSWER_ATAO 
				WHERE (DateLastModified >= <FROMDATE_Q> )
			') as a
SSIS_SQLText:
SELECT		
answer_id, 
version, 
description, 
guuid, 
CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated,  
createdby, 
CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified, 
lastmodifiedby, 
ss_external_id, 
<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
FROM answer_atao 
WHERE (datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

INSERT INTO [DataWarehouse].[Stage].[aTao_EVerify_Info]
		([EVerifyInfo_Id]
		,[Version]
		,[CaseNumber]
		,[EligibilityCode]
		,[EligibilityCodeDS]
		,[EligibilityDesc]
		,[HiringMgrName]
		,[HiringMgrComments]
		,[HiringMgrPhone]
		,[ContactDhsByDate]
		,[JobBid_Id]
		,[DateCreated]
		,[DateLastModified]
		,[CreatedBy]
		,[LastModifiedBy]
		,[ExtractDate]
		,[BatchDate]
		,[SourceSkey])
	SELECT
		[EVerifyInfo_Id]
		,[Version]
		,[CaseNumber]
		,[EligibilityCode]
		,[EligibilityCodeDS]
		,[EligibilityDesc]
		,[HiringMgrName]
		,[HiringMgrComments]
		,[HiringMgrPhone]
		,[ContactDhsByDate]
		,[JobBid_Id]
		,[DateCreated]
		,[DateLastModified]
		,[CreatedBy]
		,[LastModifiedBy]
		,<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate
		,<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate
		,<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey
	FROM OPENQUERY(<LINKNAME>, N'
		SELECT
			everifyinfo_id
			,version
			,casenumber
			,eligibilitycode
			,eligibilitycodeds
			,eligibilitydesc
			,hiringmgrname
			,hiringmgrcomments
			,hiringmgrphone
			,TO_CHAR(contactdhsbydate,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS contactdhsbydate
			,jobbid_id
			,TO_CHAR(datecreated,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS datecreated
			,TO_CHAR(datelastmodified,''YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'') AS datelastmodified
			,createdby
			,lastmodifiedby
		FROM everify_info
		WHERE
			(DateLastModified >= <FROMDATE_Q> )
		') as a
SSIS_SQLText:
SELECT		everifyinfo_id, 
				version, 
				casenumber, 
				eligibilitycode, 
				eligibilitycodeds, 
				eligibilitydesc, 
				hiringmgrname, 
				hiringmgrcomments, 
				hiringmgrphone,
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), contactdhsbydate, 120) as contactdhsbydate,  
				jobbid_id, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified, 
				createdby, 
				lastmodifiedby, 
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM everify_info 
	 WHERE (datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

SELECT /*+ index(jbr IX_JOBBID_RESP_DATEMOD) index(r SYS_C009206) */ 
				jbr.jobbid_response_id, 
				jbr.version, 
				jbr.script_id, 
				jbr.response_id, 
				jbr.jobbid_id, 
				--Grab the text for the answer if it is for a Datameaning that does not have a standard answer value (like Birth Date)
				case when q.datameaning_id IS NOT NULL and r.answer_id IS NULL then DBMS_LOB.SUBSTR(jbr.answer,255) 
				else '' end answer,				
				jbr.responsegroup, 
				TO_CHAR(jbr.datecreated,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') as datecreated, 
				TO_CHAR(jbr.datelastmodified,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') as datelastmodified, 
				jbr.createdby, 
				jbr.lastmodifiedby, 
				jbr.responserank, 
				jbr.workflowinstance_id, 
				jbr.nodeinstance_id, 
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM jobbid_response jbr 
	 INNER JOIN response_atao r 
	 ON jbr.response_id=r.response_id
	 INNER JOIN script_question_atao sq
	 ON sq.script_id = jbr.script_id AND sq.question_id = r.question_id 
	 INNER JOIN question_atao q ON r.question_id = q.question_id
	 WHERE (q.datameaning_id IS NOT NULL) 
		AND jbr.datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>
		AND jbr.datelastmodified <= <TODATE_Q>

SELECT	Opening_Inventory_Id,
		Version,
		Opening_Id,
		ClosedDate,
		HiredJobBid_Id,
		Client_Id,
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as DateCreated,  
		CreatedBy, 
		<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
		<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
		<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM Opening_Inventory 
	 WHERE (datecreated >= <FROMDATE_Q> OR ClosedDate >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

SELECT	job_history_log_id, 
		version, 
		parent, 
		parent_id, 
		client_id, 
		audit_entity, 
		entity_id, 
		alternate_id, 
		action, 
		attribute, 
		locale_id, 
		transaction_id, 
		--DBMS_LOB.SUBSTR(old_value,1000,1) as old_value, 
		--DBMS_LOB.SUBSTR(new_value,1000,1) as new_value, 
		CAST(old_value AS NVARCHAR(2000)) as old_value, 
	    CAST(new_value AS NVARCHAR(2000)) as new_value, 
		mailsent, 
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
		createdby, 
		<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
		<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
		<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM job_history_log  
	 WHERE (datecreated >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

SELECT		NonHireable_Id,
                Version,
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), NonHireExpiry, 120) as NonHireExpiry,
                SSN,
                Client_Id,
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated, 
			    CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified,
				CreatedBy, 
				LastModifiedBy, 
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM nonhireable
NULL

SELECT		CLIENTINTEGRATION_ID,
				VERSION,
				CLIENTEXT_ID,
				VENDORINTEGRATION_ID,
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as DATECREATED, 
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as DATELASTMODIFIED,
				CREATEDBY,
				LASTMODIFIEDBY,
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM CLIENTINTEGRATION 
	 WHERE (DATELASTMODIFIED >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

SELECT		PA_SCORE_ID, 
				DESCRIPTION, 
				COMMENTS, 
				URL, 
				RAWSCORE, 
				SCORE,
				STATUS,
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), STATUSDATE, 120) as STATUSDATE,
				PERCENTILE,
				LANGUAGE,
				SCRIPTSCORE_ID,
				EXTERNALID,
				ISLATEST,
				SORTVALUE,
				ASSESSMENTNAME,
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM PA_SCORE 
	 WHERE (STATUSDATE >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

SELECT	jobbid_id, 
		client_id, 
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), date_purged_utc, 120) as date_purged_utc,
		document_id, 
		userinfo_id, 
		<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
		<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
		<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM post_purge  
	 WHERE (date_purged_utc >(select top 1 DATE_PURGED_UTC_HWM from post_purge_hwm where process_name='Analytics'))

SELECT		VENDORINTEGRATION_ID,                    
				VERSION,                                 
				VENDOR_NAME,                                                                                          
				INTEGRATION_TYPE,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
				INTERNAL_NAME,                                                                                                                  
				SCRIPTCATEGORY,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
				CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datecreated, 120) as datecreated,  
			    CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), datelastmodified, 120) as datelastmodified,         
				CREATEDBY,                               
				LASTMODIFIEDBY,                          
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM VENDORINTEGRATION 
	 WHERE (DATELASTMODIFIED >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

SELECT		/*+ INDEX (SS IX_SCRIPTSCORE_DATEMOD) */	fs.PA_FACTORSCORE_ID, 
				fs.FACTORNAME, 
				fs.DESCRIPTION, 
				fs.COMMENTS, 
				fs.RAWSCORE, 
				fs.FACTORSCORE,
				fs.PA_SCORE_ID,
				fs.PERCENTILE,
				fs.TRAITBAND,
				<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
				<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
				<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	 FROM PA_FACTORSCORE fs 
	 JOIN SCRIPTSCORE ss 
	 ON fs.PA_FACTORSCORE_ID = ss.SCRIPTSCORE_ID
	 WHERE (ss.DATELASTMODIFIED >= <FROMDATE_Q>)

SELECT	Opening_Audit_Id,
		Version,
		Opening_Id,
		Action,
		Attribute,
		Transaction_Id,
		 Old_Value,
		 New_Value,
		Client_Id,
		CONVERT(VARCHAR(19), DateCreated, 120) as DateCreated, 
		CreatedBy,
		<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
		<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
		<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
FROM Opening_Audit 
WHERE (datecreated >= <FROMDATE_Q>) 
AND   attribute in ('endDate', 'status')

SELECT	SPONSOREDJOB_ID
	,POSTING_ID
	,JOBBOARDNAME
	,ACTION
	,SPONSOREDJOBSTATUS
	,STATUS
	,SERVICEID
	,SETID
	,ORDERID
    ,CONVERT(    VARCHAR(19),     DATETOPROCESS,     120  ) DATETOPROCESS
	,JOBTYPE
	,ISSHOWCOMPENSATION
	,CONVERT(    VARCHAR(19),     STARTDATE,     120  ) JOBSTARTDATE
    ,CONVERT(    VARCHAR(19),     ENDDATE,     120  ) JOBENDDATE
	,CLIENT_ID
	,LOCATION_ID
	,VERSION
	,CONVERT(    VARCHAR(19),     datecreated,     120  ) datecreated
    ,CONVERT(    VARCHAR(19),     datelastmodified,     120  ) datelastmodified
	,CREATEDBY
	,LASTMODIFIEDBY
	,<BATCHDATE> as ExtractDate, 
	<BATCHDATE> as BatchDate, 
	<SOURCESKEY> as SourceSkey 
	FROM sponsoredjob 
	WHERE (datelastmodified >= <FROMDATE_Q>)
